<codeline><highlight class="normal">sh<sp/>-c<sp/>&quot;$(curl<sp/>-fsSL<sp/>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Byson94/plug-in-c.ewwii/refs/heads/main/plugc-ewwii/install.sh)&quot;</highlight></codeline>
